{"tid":1798471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本人謹代表全體連登仔 原諒大門橫丁並希望能夠成為第二間龍門","createTime":"2019-12-26T08:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T16:32:36.000Z","uid":40867,"like":18,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b93cdc296279e5aa148284f04e24ac775f8e6df5","tid":1798471,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"既然係手足靈堂慶祝都可以原諒<br />\n既然手足比人拉當笑話都可以原諒<br />\n<br />\n原諒埋大門橫丁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地都道歉左啦屌你老母閪<br />\n<br />\njer住人做咩姐<br />\n原諒師技能發動！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不分化！！！<br />\n<br />\n原諒了！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZYNUUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZYNUUh.jpg&h=ce616029&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOKJteh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOKJteh.jpg&h=da2f5aa5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZzTx50Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzTx50Z.png&h=42250307&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/br1WOej.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbr1WOej.jpg&h=04c2a0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acPNasF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacPNasF.png&h=2a7457d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便同你班撚樣強調下<br />\n<br />\n呢兩條留言<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全部都係你地一手一腳正評出黎架on9</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n遲d原諒埋黑警啦屌你老母臭閪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拍片道歉？<br />\n捐錢道歉？？<br />\n冇啊 乜撚都冇啊 得把傻閪口渣<br />\n<br />\n依家太子班撚樣開緊party屌緊閪<br />\n個d所謂同學繼續圍威喂玩欺凌<br />\n你地慢慢抗爭啦 原諒！"},{"pid":"3707ac68e69dc623330dcd845c104e78fdca7f2e","tid":1798471,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"原諒了！！<br />\